"details/109474628"
msgstr ""
"After power-on, the Bluetooth signal can be found. https://blog.csdn.net/"
"Boantong_/article/details/109474628"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:41
#: ce439155ba464e36b2b941b283a3d58b
msgid "TB系列与PB系列在软件上能否兼容使用？"
msgstr "Are the TB series and PB series software-compatible?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:42
#: 81d7a5be84e546c881fe08528685b7ce
msgid "程序不兼容，但是BLE测试软件可以使用同一个"
msgstr ""
"The programs are not compatible, but the BLE test software can be the same."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:45
#: 61d02395b9a24882982527d060e6c00e
msgid "TB系列模组中SIGMESH协议跟私有MESH协议有什么区别？"
msgstr ""
"What is the difference between the SIG Mesh protocol and the private MESH "
"protocol in TB series modules?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:46
#: 869235e64f6044e595bc69e7e8774531
msgid ""
"SIGMESH协议的特点就是协议统一，所有采用SIGMESH协议的设备都采用了其中一套协"
"议。而私有MESH则是协议独立。"
msgstr ""
"The characteristic of the SIG Mesh protocol is that the protocol is unified; "
"all devices using the SIG Mesh protocol adopt the same protocol set. A "
"private Mesh protocol is independent."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:50
#: 2db8117519514e5b8f46f2a5340260af
msgid "PB-03F模组一包数据最大支持大多？"
msgstr "What is the maximum size of one packet supported by the PB-03F module?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:51
#: 900a9e05af56445cb5982aaf38e45f7c
msgid "TB/PB系列模组一包数据的大小由MTU参数决定，最大支持254B。"
msgstr ""
"The size of one packet for TB/PB series modules is determined by the MTU "
"parameter, with a maximum support of 254 bytes."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:54
#: 53fbc4c947f0452c81c34ca261b53831
msgid "PB01/02模组连接天猫精灵在设置三元组有哪些注意的地方"
msgstr ""
"What should be noted when setting the triplet for connecting PB01/02 modules "
"to Tmall Genie?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:55
#: ca016e02feac41a08542de4f8181af1c
msgid ""
"设备ID需要通过在线转换工具将十进制转换成十六进制并在前面补00凑够8个字节长度"
msgstr ""
"The device ID needs to be converted from decimal to hexadecimal using an "
"online conversion tool, and prefixed with 00 to make it 8 bytes long."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:58
#: 1d9811fe9d8d45dba751ed14c2a3c088
msgid "蓝牙调试助手可以给TB-02开发板发送AT指令控制IO口的电平吗"
msgstr ""
"Can the Bluetooth debugging assistant send AT commands to the TB-02 "
"development board to control the IO pin level?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:59
#: 3444e8d54928467388161d0de5d8243a
msgid "出厂AT固件不支持，需要对AT固件做二次开发实现"
msgstr ""
"The factory AT firmware does not support this. Secondary development of the "
"AT firmware is required."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:62
#: 5b2a865229124c14873c127c0b732588
msgid "PB-03F模组支持BLE5.0么？"
msgstr "Does the PB-03F module support BLE 5.0?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:63
#: 21daace1ef7a4175a9316011bbb02822
msgid "支持，PB-03系列模组支持BLE5.2，该协议向下兼容；"
msgstr ""
"Yes. The PB-03 series modules support BLE 5.2, and the protocol is backward "
"compatible."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:66
#: 4664d24334c04cb7a9940e954a9d1f67
msgid "如何实现手机控制TB-02的LED开关？"
msgstr "How can a mobile phone control the LED switch of TB-02?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:67
#: eaddd4afe10141109fd9263b6690d9fd
msgid "调用GPIO相关指令即可操作LED等的开关状态。"
msgstr ""
"Call GPIO-related commands to control the on/off state of LEDs and others."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:70
#: abcc3d84c1c24208af7838660d97b583
msgid "PB-02能传音乐吗"
msgstr "Can PB-02 transmit music?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:71
#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:273
#: 2592dfae44964918912408088ba1d2d1 c192aa43c42649589c185d5d871739a4
msgid "不能，该蓝牙没有音频芯片"
msgstr "No. This Bluetooth module does not have an audio chip."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:74
#: 3501e782c7b64822bcfea123bfd0d2ed
msgid "PB03出厂默认AT固件最长能设置蓝牙广播名称为多少个字节"
msgstr ""
"What is the maximum Bluetooth advertising name length supported by the "
"default factory AT firmware of PB-03?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:75
#: abda3c6aa77848cb980f3c2c27ca4c7c
msgid "12个字节"
msgstr "12 bytes."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:78
#: 09344625867c401c9767410fd23b1fac
msgid "PB-01、02如何对接天猫精灵"
msgstr "How do PB-01 and PB-02 connect to Tmall Genie?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:79
#: 424b896d52f642069aa23be22913643c
msgid "烧写支持对接天猫精灵固件并通过指令设置天猫精灵平台提供的三元组"
msgstr ""
"Flash the firmware that supports Tmall Genie integration, and set the "
"triplet provided by the Tmall Genie platform through commands."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:82
