#: 9796ef46dfbf4d589a14722aea391ec9
msgid "默认天线采用半孔焊盘方式，可以在主板上设计一个IPEX端口方便进行外接"
msgstr ""
"By default, the antenna uses a castellated solder pad design. You can design "
"an IPEX port on the mainboard for external antenna connection."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:87
#: e0a9585b5ff14f0f8bdc08b418924d9f
msgid "PB系列的SDK代码用什么开发平台"
msgstr "What development platform is used for the PB series SDK code?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:88
#: e29b60ec515a49fb82027626a70acd33
