#: 089cac6d3f8b44ff94d68dea40c1e535
msgid ""
"该模组具有透传功能，详情参考说明文档。该模组支持二次开发，详情访问我司官方"
"DOCS系统。"
msgstr ""
"This module has transparent transmission functionality. For details, refer "
"to the user manual. The module supports secondary development. For details, "
"visit our official DOCS system."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:144
#: f392500e1f024df0a62fcd51217f3c1a
msgid "请问下PB-03可以二次开发么，用的哪一个开发环境呢？"
msgstr ""
"Can PB-03 be secondarily developed? Which development environment is used?"

