#: 1b4592439d874af88e034c2d693f0cf1
msgid "支持二次开发，用的开发环境是keil MDK。"
msgstr ""
"Yes, it supports secondary development. The development environment is Keil "
"MDK."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:148
#: b39b870c40384185a60573be8af12070
msgid "TB-04模组能否与其他蓝牙设备进行通讯？"
msgstr "Can the TB-04 module communicate with other Bluetooth devices?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:149
#: 60adfb33b6034f188b436e7284c80a55
msgid "通过二次开发可以实现；"
