#: 53de506a80e547e5aef5ea5e04166e94
msgid "目前仅支持天猫精灵音响"
msgstr "Currently, only Tmall Genie speakers are supported."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:156
#: 740238eb25774d89826997d3359fec2a
msgid "请问一下PB-03F的RX0、TX0串口电平是TTL还是232？"
