#: e71f84e310f44c2a8a67f4b403a0004d
msgid "是TTL电平"
msgstr "They are TTL levels."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:160
#: e3132717d10540d88dd75bf7acac8621
msgid "TB/PB系列模块可以跟电脑通信吗"
msgstr "Can TB/PB series modules communicate with a computer?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:161
#: 44afc332509c41fbb22ab1e309ee7001
msgid "可以，不过需要购买专门的蓝牙适配器进行调试"
msgstr ""
"Yes, but a dedicated Bluetooth adapter needs to be purchased for debugging."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:164
#: 3bad6a7e6a504495bef61ac08c48de7b
msgid "PB-02模组上的RST引脚复位是高电平还是低电平"
msgstr "Is the RST pin reset of the PB-02 module active-high or active-low?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:168
#: cfa68ad87bff4fb1bd677e4348f5f300
msgid "PB-03F模组在烧录固件过程中掉电了，有办法恢复么？"
msgstr ""
"If the PB-03F module loses power during firmware flashing, is there a way to "
"recover it?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:169
#: 2cd80197abf94337a2d26f216dbd986d
msgid "重新刷固件即可"
msgstr "Just flash the firmware again."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:172
#: 26172768c4fb499c9f0618836d4cb7bc
msgid "TB系列模组支持OTA升级吗"
msgstr "Do TB series modules support OTA upgrade?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:173
#: 7548a29527ff4c8c9553c5c2de732772
msgid "支持，可以通过APP的方式进行升级"
msgstr "Yes, they can be upgraded via an app."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:176
#: 35be6c33339a436f8c120c523928a2b9
msgid "请问一下，PB-03F模组二次开发，GPIO中断能用吗？"
msgstr ""
"For secondary development of the PB-03F module, can GPIO interrupts be used?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/bt/bt.rst:180
#: b83cbd3aaa38456c938138dc313b1dd4
msgid "你好，请问一下PB-03F模组在刷机的时候掉电了，还能回复吗？"
msgstr ""
"If the PB-03F module loses power during flashing, can it still be recovered?"

